# Benefits

• Lower API cost

• Offline capability

• Predictable behaviour

• Continuous local learning

• Smaller code complexity

• Easier testing

• Vendor independence

---

# Consequences

Batman becomes progressively more capable without increasing LLM dependence.

Every future feature shall use the Understanding Engine before business logic executes.

